mg src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-15T07:09:40.000Z","msg":"高文英本人<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-15T07:12:24.000Z","msg":"原來嗰陣只係演返自己<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b8cc99a5b400103425503892f089d71896b0232a","tid":2489401,"uid":310700,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"7bd79f8e717268c3c87bef5d518f4db9725f1fcc","tid":2489401,"uid":36040,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"6ad4e3c6b31597dfda9d42b16cabea09b228d6d8","tid":2489401,"uid":310700,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"0849ebf560ea72fc286a2c49e9ffff483348c36c","tid":2489401,"uid":58335,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2021-04-15T07:02:25.000Z","msg":"呢條癲婆搞撚死埋金正賢演藝生涯<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-15T07:09:40.000Z","msg":"高文英本人<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-15T07:12:24.000Z","msg":"原來嗰陣只係演返自己<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-15T07:13:30.000Z","msg":"唔怪得演得咁自然<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a6b94b5a55c35e61f3cbe0e69a2ea94b6db48cf4","tid":2489401,"uid":58335,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"b8cc99a5b400103425503892f089d71896b0232a","tid":2489401,"uid":310700,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"7bd79f8e717268c3c87bef5d518f4db9725f1fcc","tid":2489401,"uid":36040,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"6ad4e3c6b31597dfda9d42b16cabea09b228d6d8","tid":2489401,"uid":310700,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-15T07:09:40.000Z","msg":"高文英本人<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-15T07:12:24.000Z","msg":"原來嗰陣只係演返自己<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-15T07:13:30.000Z","msg":"唔怪得演得咁自然<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-15T07:21:04.000Z","msg":"最近有網友挖出《精神病》播出時導演的採訪，當初導演表示，<span class=\"red\">高文英不好演，因為她不但具有反社會人格，</span>但同時還有悲傷的過去。演表示，<span class=\"red\">他第一眼見到徐睿知時就覺得：「高文英就是她！」</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />馬上就決定讓徐睿知扮演高文英。<br />\n<br />\n而徐睿知也有相似的行為，徐睿知曾在《認哥》分享，小時候她家去爬山，她和姊姊玩遊戲。姊姊是背著前方走路的，徐睿知看到姊姊快掉下去，本來應該要叫姊姊注意後面，但她一緊張，腦袋難以反應直接說了：「剪刀石頭布」，而姊姊真的掉了下去。<br />\n<br />\n最近網友挖出徐睿知在《另有他路》的採訪，發現兩人根本一模一樣！當時劇本有一場「醉酒開車」的戲份，徐睿知負責開車，金材昱坐在副駕駛<br />\n<br />\n徐睿知為了讓整場戲更逼真，<span class=\"red\">直接把車開出雙黃線，結果對面方向一台巴士開過來，差點出車禍！金材昱表示，當時徐睿知看起來真的很享受，邊開還嘻嘻哈哈，「就像瘋了一樣」。</span><br />\n<br />\n徐睿知說，當時真的以為姊姊快死了，後來有一位路過的大叔救下姊姊。細節徐睿知忘了，但她說姊姊直到長大後都還一直對這件事很生氣，因為當時姊姊上來後，她沒有很擔心姊姊，反而對大叔的兒子自我介紹說：「你好我是徐睿知」。<br />\n<br />\n雖然可能有綜藝效果，但徐睿知全程嘻笑地說著姊姊生命危險的故事，<span class=\"red\">而她在故事中「腦袋無法反應害姊姊掉下山」、「對大叔兒子自我介紹」的反應都讓網友覺得很不合常理、沒有同理心。</span><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.beauty321.com/post/39855#p3\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.beauty321.com%2Fpost%2F39855%23p3&d=RjdfG9uxtkM%2FelS3aO62sEwFe44qEnauMGuWilFD6Zg%3D&h=4cbf2d26\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.beauty321.com/post/39855#p3</a>"},{"pid":"c52b77ca3a4d333b70641a670104a958f3073fed","tid":2489401,"uid":208486,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"0849ebf560ea72fc286a2c49e9ffff483348c36c","tid":2489401,"uid":58335,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2021-04-15T07:02:25.000Z","msg":"呢條癲婆搞撚死埋金正賢演藝生涯<